Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we have questions and answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We discovered through experience that people appreciate hearing the discussions in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.89,0:01:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened the first time by accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.96,0:01:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The microphone was on and I was talking to some people and pretty soon there's a whole
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.20,0:01:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,crowd around and people said, let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.81,0:01:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Next year we'll probably increase the length of the questions and discussions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have a less didactic presentation because that's all appeared in books.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.43,0:01:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You see I present it as I write it and much of what I present won't appear in print for
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.59,0:01:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,a year or two, but as it's available in print then we'll spend more time in traditional
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,exchange between everyone and we can answer things in greater depth and greater length.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.51,0:01:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll spend more time with questions and answers and discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.15,0:01:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And we may figure out a different way of doing it other than lining up, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:02:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so let's be happy to proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I put the books on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.40,0:02:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you have to kind of talk into the mic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.88,0:02:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Which mic is the one he talks into?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.88,0:02:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, both of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.88,0:02:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.88,0:02:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.88,0:02:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.88,0:02:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.88,0:02:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.88,0:02:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the question is about the collapse of the waveform.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.88,0:02:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.43,0:02:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about the energy of the virtual reality and over the decades what we've heard is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that where the collapse takes place is in machines or something, but my conclusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is where?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.65,0:02:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In machines, devices like the spectrograph, whatever else.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Collapse, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.75,0:02:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.75,0:02:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They were trying to figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My own conclusion is that the collapse takes place in consciousness and the question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,if that is so, what does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:03:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any such thing as reality of particles or is that in a...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a perception of our consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's perception, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.15,0:03:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Perception of the consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Because, of course, sub-particle physics is speaking only of potential energies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really only talking about potentialities and, you know, we were talking about the actualization
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of potential and that is sort of an explanation of the mechanics, the mechanics of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The potential is activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on the power of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, because consciousness is infinitely powerful, therefore creation is the emergence of the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,unmanifest into the manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.18,0:03:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Manifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that is how creation comes about because the field is so powerful, any possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:03:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,then becomes an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then matter is really just an illusion of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a little difficult to answer because of the way you phrased it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You said nothing but.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.03,0:04:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't nothing but.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Because things are multi-dimensional, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Potentiality at one level.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.02,0:04:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's energy at another.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's empty space, you know, because an atom is 99.9% empty space, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.82,0:04:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,One electron hovering around claims that territory for itself, but it's really empty space.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.82,0:04:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,99% of the solid world is actually empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, thank you, first of all, for continuing to write and have these seminars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we all appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.68,0:05:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly do, so thank you both very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, should spiritual students do everything that we can to take some stewardship
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,over the other species on the planet that are being so negatively harmed by other humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,or should we just leave it to God?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, it's a projection of perception, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dalai Lama said, no, it wasn't the Dalai Lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Mahatma Gandhi, one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the skinnier one, I forget which one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Sir will know the answer to this one, which one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He said, it is not enough to just pray for yourself, pray for yourself, but to do everything
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you can to be of assistance to life in the world, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What you can do to be of assistance to life in the world, it depends on your level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,At one level of consciousness, you give it beneficial neglect and let it be what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,At another level, you see suffering and you wish to intervene.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that from the viewpoint of compassion, one does all one can to relieve suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, suffering is the way to redemption for the undoingness of negative karma,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.06,0:06:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the undoing of the agony you've caused others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You experience now what that was like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the next time you don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:07:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it would be where one is in one's karmic evolution, which you feel called upon to do by the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I think whatever you consider to be the most compassionate would be the best, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Like eliminating your enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The mind is very clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Justify anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I would also like to thank you for the gift of continued teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.67,0:07:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and to use your term, recontextualizing my spirit life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, thank you very much for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My question, I've seen or heard you or read about the etheric body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You also mentioned the Christ or Atmic body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:08:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The causal body, Buddhic body, Christ body, Atmic body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are classic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Buddhic, Christ, Atmic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are above the physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They are energy fields which are taught about in esoteric psychology.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Esoteric psychology.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Energy congregations, you might say the attractor fields of the spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,in contradistinction to the attractor fields of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the lower mind, higher mind, causal body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There's people who know more about it than I do here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I just use it for general reference, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.09,0:08:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a spiritual discernment that accompanies the opening of the third eye of the Buddhic body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, each of these bodies also has what's comparable to chakra system
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,which when you get into really high realms over the 800
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:09:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,is what you're pulling up from the unconscious all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when you're comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when you're comfortable, you feel a terrible pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's some aspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And instead of looking for it in your personal life, you won't find it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll find it in the collective unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I know when I wrote Truth vs. Falsehood, I had a lot of trouble with the spiritual knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The spiritual knight came up with indignation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Look what they've done to God's truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had to quiet the spiritual knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But the spiritual knight was indignant because I'd ignored the world for a long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, except the small space of clinical practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But the world itself I'd ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, now I thought, well, we'll apply this calibrating of levels of truth to the world as it appears
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and see what shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And up came the spiritual knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the collective.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:09:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Indignant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Indignant, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that took some correction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,After one has had the grace of a guru and the transmission of no mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and one fully intuitively understands all the material presented,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is it necessary for one to continue the classes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Classes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Being here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.16,0:10:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you would do it for the purposes of being with the people you love and care for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.05,0:10:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to it because...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.48,0:10:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like family week, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.03,0:11:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My first time to see you and hear you was very impressed that you came around
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and touched everyone and said hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question to you is really about touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Your thoughts on those who have suffered trauma
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.03,0:11:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,when touch is compassionate, intentional, and reverent, its value to consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.46,0:11:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was trying to make it a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The value of touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I never really calibrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The touch is expressive of the love I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,To make it experiential on a sensory level.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.61,0:11:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's symbolic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether innately it has something of itself, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I never asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:12:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have permission to ask that here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The actual touch has some additional benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A significant value of resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I never knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I just did it intuitively, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran out of peacock feathers to hit people with,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so I guess I'll have to get them on space.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.17,0:12:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.17,0:12:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Several times you've mentioned Ramana Maharshi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.17,0:12:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,in your lectures and books.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering his teaching of self-inquiry,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,if that's the most direct path.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I've written about it in the last two books
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,which aren't in print yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-inquiry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've not been impressed by the consequences of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.62,0:13:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I get the intention of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The difficulty with it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it starts out with the pronoun who
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and then it asks the pronoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're looking for a who
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,when the answer is a what.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So I say, in the book, Ramana Maharshi taught,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And I find it more fruitful to ask, what am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when you get rid of the personal identification
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,as the pronoun I,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.70,0:13:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you move to the witness-observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the witness-observer,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,what is the witness-observer coming out of?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, those are not who's, those are what's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.70,0:13:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,See, witnessing happens spontaneously, autonomously.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:14:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no who witnessing, and that dawns on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The witnessing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So you move from identification with content
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to that which is witnessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you move to the observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it dawns on you there isn't any observer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,or nor witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That there is a quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're a quality, you're not a who.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,By what quality are you conscious or aware?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you see that's impersonal,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that that's a quality of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.23,0:14:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're not a who, you're the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm always afraid, by asking who,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that you're going to be looking for another pronoun,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,a different definition of self,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe more sophisticated,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but still a definition.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This time you're looking for a definition of self
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,with a capital S,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.19,0:14:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,which is at least in the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:15:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,However, inferential in his works,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the analogy I think he had of the camera, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The film?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, the screen and the film.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.35,0:15:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what's witnessed there on the TV set.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I just think it's more fruitful to ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,what is it that is observing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that's experiencing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that's witnessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm afraid the word who
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.55,0:15:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is constricting to a pronoun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking for another pronoun, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,With the full potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so that's why I appreciate what he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll tweak it a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I also, but I do second his,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,what he called the fourth state,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,which I rediscovered and then discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I already defined it, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:16:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that you won't find the infinite between thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You find it in the field out of which all of thought arises.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So you look to the underlying field
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and the underlying field is silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And with observation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and sort of a contemplative lifestyle,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.72,0:16:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you become one with the silent,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.97,0:16:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,with the silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So you walk around,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,not in the state of sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.27,0:16:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,not in the state of slated dreaming,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,not in an ordinary state,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but in a state in which
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you are the infinite silence
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which all form arises.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's present in this room right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.12,0:16:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you look underneath your thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll find that nothing's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still and silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You learn to live in the fourth state.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, so I value his work
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,because he gave it a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Turiya, Turiya, Turiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.27,0:17:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanskrit Turiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the fourth state of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Not sleeping, not dreaming, not awake,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.44,0:17:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,but aware, conscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but without form or content.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just being. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.71,0:17:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, so young to be so advanced in curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, my question sort of follows
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,on Lindsay's question and that is,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is it true what some Advaita teachers say
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that personal free will is an illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.79,0:17:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that the only real choice you have
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is to move towards that fourth state of consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is to move towards what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the fourth state of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.79,0:17:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The fourth state, fourth?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Fourth, or more of a witness consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:17:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,is the only true choice that you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.79,0:18:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's sort of a constrictive definition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really a little more complicated than that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,because in the same vein,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.72,0:18:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you could say there isn't such a thing as karma,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,which on a certain level is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's true for you, it's true for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.88,0:18:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but if it ain't, watch out because...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, well, karma is just an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.88,0:18:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.99,0:18:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Personal free will is an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.99,0:18:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, personal free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, personal free will,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,of course, that is the term.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All it means is that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you're constantly presented with options
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and choices and they're continuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're like the prow of the ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,which is constantly making adjustments.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to constantly go here or there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the experiencer who is out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.21,0:18:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and the experiencer is constantly searching,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.21,0:18:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,searching, searching,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,so that a decision has to be made all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.21,0:19:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can eat this, this is poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a friend, this is a foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can mate with this, it'll reject me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.21,0:19:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,See what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's constantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's constantly searching
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's constantly has to make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.66,0:19:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to move in one direction or the other, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when the ego is predominant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's not predominant,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.95,0:19:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the ship goes however the wind and the seas set it, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.95,0:19:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And what controls it is intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So a decision of the will
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.95,0:19:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,is like setting your karmic compass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, once you set your karmic compass now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,it will go this way and that way
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,with the waves and the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.75,0:19:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're not going to change your compass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your compass is set.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way to fall in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is to make a bad decision by the spiritual will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So we talk about in these classes sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but maybe later on in the books on completing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,also the temptations and the traps,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,because that which goes up can also go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can make serious errors to fall for adulation,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.93,0:20:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,control over others, money,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,glamour, sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the ones that pull them all down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.93,0:20:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They're on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.59,0:20:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So you'd say there are choices
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and that personal free will does exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.52,0:20:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise there'd be no karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're responsible to the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,for every decision, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you're responsible, you're culpable
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to the degree of your knowingness at that level.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.68,0:20:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So you could make what is really not a spiritual error,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but because you believe it is a sin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and you went and did it anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,now you've got a negative karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.72,0:20:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you saw it from up here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd realize there was nothing wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So from a certain state of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:20:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,suddenly, like you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.72,0:21:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you're just going with spontaneity
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and kind of off the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the kind of decisions you're making
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,are based on your spiritual alignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you live a life, your life is a prayer,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,then you dedicate your life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.16,0:21:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,to appreciating the beauty of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.16,0:21:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the sacredness of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.16,0:21:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the support of the happiness of others,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.44,0:21:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and being a servant of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So to be a servant of God already
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,defines somewhat your role as to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.44,0:21:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, through prayer, you may get, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,to go and do something to feed the hungry,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.29,0:21:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,or you may get allowing them to experience
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the hunger that you cause the others
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.72,0:21:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,through your selfishness, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know what it is to be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So the rich aristocrat that's, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.31,0:21:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that ignore the starvation of the population
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.76,0:22:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,while they indulge themself in massive indulgences
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.02,0:22:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,has something to learn,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.02,0:22:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,what it is to be hungry and desperate and poor
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.02,0:22:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and chased by the police all at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.27,0:22:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So beheading probably helped them learn that lesson,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.84,0:22:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but probably not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, consider the arrogance of that lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.23,0:22:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The beheading didn't make any difference either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.00,0:22:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, so, yeah, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.00,0:22:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So it depends on what your level is,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.00,0:22:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the karma involved, the level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So the options have a certain range, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A frog cannot decide to become a bird, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've only got a limited range
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.00,0:22:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,due to karmic propensities to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.59,0:22:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll notice that you have to,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you're making decisions all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.59,0:22:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,either wittingly or unwittingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.59,0:22:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're driving a car,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.59,0:22:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you're making constant adjustments, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.18,0:23:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, your steering wheel never just stays still.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.18,0:23:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll soon be off the road,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.18,0:23:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're constantly making little adjustments.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.18,0:23:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what your mind is doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.18,0:23:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,making little adjustments to smile sweetly,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.33,0:23:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to smile not so sweetly,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.33,0:23:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to not look too friendly,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.33,0:23:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,or to give them a scowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you've got to make up your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.63,0:23:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, coming to you with a hat, you've got to decide,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.63,0:23:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,go away, or give them a quarter,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.03,0:23:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,or get a job, bum, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.03,0:23:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.03,0:23:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got all kinds of options.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.03,0:23:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.03,0:23:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It just seems like at a certain point,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.03,0:23:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not a conscious decision anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.03,0:23:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's just like things are just happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.17,0:23:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes, it goes on automatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.17,0:23:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So one of the spiritual practices is to watch and be aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.29,0:23:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Nisargadatta Maharaj, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.29,0:23:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,reached enlightenment, I think, three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.29,0:23:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dictum was really to watch the mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.29,0:23:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't say do anything with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.29,0:23:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,don't correct it, but watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.29,0:23:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what we said today, the Heisenberg principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.29,0:23:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you merely watch a certain behavior,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.29,0:23:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,it will automatically diminish,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.29,0:24:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's a behavior you don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.68,0:24:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a behavior you do like,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.68,0:24:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,watching it will tend to increase it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.68,0:24:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Expect a miracle is a saying, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.68,0:24:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you expect a miracle,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.68,0:24:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the more likely it is, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.68,0:24:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,by the Heisenberg principle,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.68,0:24:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's going to precipitate it out of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.68,0:24:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But that, again, is dependent on karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.27,0:24:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.27,0:24:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I, too, want to thank you for being available.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.90,0:24:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is about a daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.90,0:24:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of mine who has really severe depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.90,0:24:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you had all the shame,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.90,0:24:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,attractions, and aversions up there,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.90,0:24:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized that every single one
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.90,0:24:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of the attractions has been present
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.90,0:24:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and kind of defined the depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.90,0:24:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is not the first time either
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.16,0:24:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that she had a major crash and has a three-year-old.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.16,0:25:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That has been completely dysfunctional
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.16,0:25:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,in treatment and will be continuing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.16,0:25:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And severe depression?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.16,0:25:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Severe, severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.16,0:25:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Intractable.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.22,0:25:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.22,0:25:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Non-responsive to any presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.53,0:25:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.53,0:25:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Jock treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.56,0:25:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Had not had jock treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.56,0:25:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.56,0:25:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I curious?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.56,0:25:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.96,0:25:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything that I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.91,0:25:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, other than prayer,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.00,0:25:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see what you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.13,0:25:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She has her own karmic propensity to run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.83,0:25:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know what the karmic background is,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.83,0:25:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but out of benevolence,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.83,0:25:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,you do all you can
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.83,0:25:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to release suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.83,0:25:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So you provide all the options
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.83,0:25:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,by which then she has to make an inner decision
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.83,0:25:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to come out of it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.83,0:25:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and to let go of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.83,0:25:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Severe depression is spiritual, psychological,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.73,0:25:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,physical, and clinical.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.73,0:26:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It produces neurotransmitters.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.99,0:26:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And when those neurotransmitters get depleted,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.99,0:26:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the person gets depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.99,0:26:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,When you build them back up again,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.07,0:26:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,generally, generally,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.07,0:26:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,they will come out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.57,0:26:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So that has to be done
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.57,0:26:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,on all those levels that you spoke of,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.57,0:26:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the physical, the spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.57,0:26:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that's physical, mental, and spiritual,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.57,0:26:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in approaching all three simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.60,0:26:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you try some powerful antidepressant,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.60,0:26:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,like a fixer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.60,0:26:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Very seldom does the depression not come out of,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.60,0:26:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,depression not affect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.60,0:26:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And you do counseling,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.60,0:26:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you do group therapy,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.60,0:26:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,spirituality, prayer,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.60,0:26:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and do everything you can
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.68,0:26:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,physically, mentally, and spiritually.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.67,0:26:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it's going to run its course.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.67,0:26:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.73,0:26:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.73,0:26:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And you talked about that intractable patient that you had,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.73,0:26:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,which means that, of course, there are some
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.73,0:26:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Intractable what?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.73,0:26:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,patients that you had
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.73,0:26:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,that just did not respond to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.73,0:26:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There was only one, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.73,0:26:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.63,0:27:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a brain made of lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.63,0:27:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.10,0:27:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not going to hold that in consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.10,0:27:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that she's intractable.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.10,0:27:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she's not intractable.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.10,0:27:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But something else came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.10,0:27:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.10,0:27:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and when this first, this crash happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.10,0:27:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, God, you know, we need an exorcist.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.10,0:27:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I mean, I honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.10,0:27:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought of everything, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.10,0:27:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I did think of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.10,0:27:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about the idea of possession
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.10,0:27:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,or another energy taking...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.29,0:27:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you try everything when you're desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.29,0:27:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.32,0:27:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,People, some people get so desperate,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.51,0:27:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,they look for a psychiatrist, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.51,0:27:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,At death's door, they call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.63,0:27:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.63,0:27:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Two weeks, they're out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.63,0:27:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.63,0:27:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years of suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.31,0:27:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have a toehold in psychiatry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.31,0:28:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I just published an article in this month,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.31,0:28:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,this week's psychiatric news
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.31,0:28:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,on antidepressants in childhood and adolescence, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.79,0:28:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.50,0:28:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.50,0:28:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you explain more about the aging process
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.50,0:28:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,or what we perceive as aging?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.50,0:28:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The aging process?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.50,0:28:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.50,0:28:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.50,0:28:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You get tired, wrinkle, gray and old,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.89,0:28:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you fall over.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.89,0:28:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.00,0:28:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a patient said to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.74,0:28:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,what if this doesn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.74,0:28:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, then you die, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.74,0:28:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But haven't you said it couldn't come from a linear process?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.24,0:28:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.24,0:28:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,From a linear process, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.88,0:28:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Physicality is linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.88,0:28:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.35,0:29:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The body arises from the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.35,0:29:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,then it returns to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.35,0:29:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was trying to make it non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.80,0:29:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I was trying to make it non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.15,0:29:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're talking about the physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.66,0:29:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The reality is non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.17,0:29:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute you're outside of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.68,0:29:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I knew that when I was 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.89,0:29:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly time stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.04,0:29:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,An infinite presence beyond all description.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.44,0:29:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Love like no human can ordinarily experience it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.46,0:29:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The divine presence was who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.46,0:29:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And as who I am, the reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.77,0:29:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I exist before all universes
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.77,0:29:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and will be after all universes have disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.77,0:30:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.39,0:30:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a fact, oh Lord, resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.39,0:30:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.76,0:30:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That which I am was before all universes
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.76,0:30:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and will be after they have all disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.64,0:30:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That takes care of linear temporality.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.64,0:30:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.91,0:30:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there's periodic reincarnations
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.16,0:30:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,for the karmic benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.16,0:30:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, there's certain contracts, I think,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.31,0:30:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that are made that I've forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.31,0:30:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of body now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.31,0:30:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In body now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.31,0:30:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.21,0:30:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So your reality is non-linear
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.58,0:30:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and it won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.72,0:30:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So the you won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.72,0:30:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The what you think you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.23,0:30:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,get rid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.39,0:30:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's still fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.86,0:30:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.44,0:31:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The body is like a karmic wind-up toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.44,0:31:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good for entertainment and fun
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.44,0:31:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and dancing and music and eating donuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.92,0:31:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Might as well juice it
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.07,0:31:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,for whatever good you can get out of it
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.07,0:31:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,when you got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.07,0:31:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you don't get attached to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.61,0:31:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't get attached to it
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.61,0:31:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and don't identify with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.75,0:31:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I think you enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.75,0:31:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You enjoy it like a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.75,0:31:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's a fun thing, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.75,0:31:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.20,0:31:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fun thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.20,0:31:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't dance or stand on your head without it, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.25,0:31:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a fun thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.19,0:31:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy it while you got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.19,0:31:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't believe that that's who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.19,0:31:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.07,0:31:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,See, because there's the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.07,0:31:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you know there's a body?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.20,0:31:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.35,0:31:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what is it that's aware of the physicality?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.49,0:31:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So instantly you withdraw from the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.49,0:31:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, you're not the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.49,0:31:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that which experiences the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.49,0:32:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're that which thinks it's experiencing the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.49,0:32:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're that which is experiencing experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.49,0:32:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see, you begin to withdraw
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.49,0:32:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,from identification with the physicality.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.49,0:32:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The physicality is limited to this dimension.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.35,0:32:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,When I rediscovered physicality, I was age three.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.59,0:32:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was not happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.01,0:32:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was not happy to have a physicality
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.91,0:32:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and find myself back in the physical domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.97,0:32:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, say goodbye to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.59,0:32:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You drop into the world and you drop out again.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.03,0:32:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In and out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.03,0:33:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a bunch of birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.94,0:33:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We come in as a flock together.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.94,0:33:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gone through this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.94,0:33:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole group here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.94,0:33:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We've all flocked here like a bunch of swans.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.94,0:33:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We've nested down and we've flown on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.94,0:33:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We tend to swoop in and swoop out pretty much together.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.23,0:33:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, the saviors such as Christ and Buddha
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.02,0:33:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and even the Holy Spirit have done and are doing
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.02,0:33:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,so much for humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.02,0:33:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering, is there anything
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.02,0:33:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that people may do for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.82,0:33:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do for whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.82,0:33:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.75,0:33:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn out of whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.01,0:33:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a quality of divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.01,0:33:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,expressed as consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.01,0:33:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,To be a servant of the Lord, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.44,0:33:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is to become all that one karmic,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.44,0:33:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to fulfill one's karmic potential
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.44,0:33:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,to the best of one's ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.47,0:33:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That pretty much fulfills your obligation,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.47,0:34:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,your gratitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.47,0:34:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and the expression of thanks for your existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.28,0:34:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,To be the best long-distance runner you can be,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.28,0:34:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,you put your heart into it
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.28,0:34:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and you take yourself right to the edge
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.28,0:34:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you break through the barrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.36,0:34:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger Bannister.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.15,0:34:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You do all that you can pull up with your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.15,0:34:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And devotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.15,0:34:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's devotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.65,0:34:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual commitment.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.65,0:34:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual will and devotion are very, very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.76,0:34:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.48,0:34:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, God doesn't need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.48,0:34:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The Holy Spirit doesn't need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.09,0:34:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The divinity delights in the fulfillment
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.09,0:34:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which you created.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.65,0:34:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You bring up a dog and teach it tricks
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.78,0:34:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see how happy and gay
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.78,0:34:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and how it's fulfilled its potential
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.78,0:34:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to learn and be a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.78,0:34:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.78,0:35:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That brings you joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.01,0:35:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.59,0:35:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That is our potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.19,0:35:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, to fulfill our karmic potentiality
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.19,0:35:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to the best of our ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.61,0:35:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,To align yourself with divine intention
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.61,0:35:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is a very powerful act of the will.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.61,0:35:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already done 90% of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.61,0:35:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest is really up to the Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.61,0:35:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to unfold to you what the options are.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.61,0:35:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, thank you for taking my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.15,0:35:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.15,0:35:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question about,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.15,0:35:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe you can share with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.15,0:35:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,about overcoming a phobia
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.15,0:35:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,from your clinical and spiritual knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.15,0:35:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Any advice about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.15,0:35:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been living with a phobia for a long time in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.15,0:35:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's not right about that
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.15,0:35:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and the level of fear, which we don't get to.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.15,0:35:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to suffer it for a couple more lectures.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.15,0:36:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we get to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.11,0:36:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear is innate to the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.11,0:36:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because it bases survival on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.11,0:36:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it attaches fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.21,0:36:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,gets programmed into certain things.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.21,0:36:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be phobic.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.21,0:36:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be afraid of open places,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.21,0:36:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,claustrophobia, agoraphobia.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.21,0:36:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A multitude of phobias.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.51,0:36:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And to recover from them,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.51,0:36:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a couple of ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.51,0:36:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The spiritual way is to suffer out the fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.51,0:36:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go resisting the fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.63,0:36:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, fear is a combination of a physiology
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.84,0:36:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,plus imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.84,0:36:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.75,0:36:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So the imagination,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.75,0:36:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you're probably not going to do much about.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.75,0:36:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But the fear, you can experience out,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.75,0:36:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.75,0:36:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It may take hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.80,0:36:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the what you're afraid of,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.28,0:36:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but the fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.28,0:36:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an experience which is sensory.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.28,0:36:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.28,0:37:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shaking of the knees,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.28,0:37:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,a whim-whammy in the stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.28,0:37:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a trembling of the nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.42,0:37:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a feeling of terror and pending doom.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.51,0:37:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.61,0:37:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the spiritual way to do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.61,0:37:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is you let go resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.67,0:37:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, all feelings have a limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.67,0:37:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not limitless.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.73,0:37:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So all the fear since the beginning of time
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.73,0:37:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,has compounded,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.73,0:37:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you have what in Esther is called a big stack.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.73,0:37:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a big stack called fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.73,0:37:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And you experience out the fear
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.15,0:37:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,without resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.15,0:37:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the way you get rid of pain too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.15,0:37:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You surrender to the fear
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.19,0:37:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and allow it to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.53,0:37:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop resisting the fear
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.53,0:37:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and stop calling it fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.53,0:37:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't experience fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.53,0:37:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only experience sensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.36,0:37:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go resisting the sensation
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.36,0:37:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and don't label it fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.36,0:37:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't experience hunger either.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.03,0:37:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hunger is a name, a label.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.03,0:38:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only experience a physicality
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.63,0:38:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,as it is arising.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.92,0:38:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can let go resisting.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.67,0:38:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And eventually you'll drain it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.07,0:38:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, at the bottom of the fears,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.07,0:38:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I call it so what.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.07,0:38:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If your fears are specific, see,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.46,0:38:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you can do the process called so what.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.46,0:38:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't get this job,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.03,0:38:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.03,0:38:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.48,0:38:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And then my friends will laugh at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.48,0:38:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.48,0:38:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I won't have any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.09,0:38:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.09,0:38:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I can't pay my mortgage.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.09,0:38:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.09,0:38:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.09,0:38:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you surrender that to God?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.09,0:38:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.80,0:38:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people say, no, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.80,0:38:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, I've got a .38 caliber bullet
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.30,0:38:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,in this revolver.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.40,0:38:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you don't surrender,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.40,0:38:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to blow your brains out.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.40,0:38:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.40,0:38:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.40,0:38:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So it isn't that you can't,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.61,0:39:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,it's that you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.61,0:39:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to blow your brains out
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.90,0:39:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,unless you let go of this, brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.90,0:39:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to let go of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.90,0:39:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have one on me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.75,0:39:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.07,0:39:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,For those who are really brave and courageous,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.07,0:39:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,there's the crash program
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.07,0:39:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,where you just allow the fears to rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.07,0:39:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's the, then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.07,0:39:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.15,0:39:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get old and I'll be old and ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.15,0:39:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And then nobody will love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.15,0:39:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I won't, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.15,0:39:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and then, and then, and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.15,0:39:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And the fear always ends up as a fear of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.15,0:39:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.15,0:39:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'll be penniless.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.15,0:39:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'll be homeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.15,0:39:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the people on the street will attack me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.32,0:39:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And they'll rob me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.32,0:39:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll be weak and old.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.32,0:39:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'll get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.32,0:39:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.32,0:39:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.32,0:39:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So once you surrender to physical death,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.28,0:39:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole stack of fear usually disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.28,0:40:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's other ways of doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.78,0:40:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Crash program, virtual reality
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.88,0:40:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in which you consciously choose a fear situation
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.90,0:40:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and recreate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.90,0:40:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Fear of flying, let's say, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.07,0:40:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's various ways you can recreate
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.23,0:40:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and extinguish it by being with the fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.44,0:40:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's fear reduction programs, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.44,0:40:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,in which what you're afraid of,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.44,0:40:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,they recreate it as a virtual reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.44,0:40:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And you let go resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.44,0:40:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, finally it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.55,0:40:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.88,0:40:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say a person has a germ phobia.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.88,0:40:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So you get the germs and then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.88,0:40:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'll get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.88,0:40:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.88,0:40:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.32,0:41:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.32,0:41:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.28,0:41:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The inevitable is inevitable,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.28,0:41:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,which means you don't want to die now instead of later.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.28,0:41:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So it isn't that you got to let go of dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.44,0:41:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to let go of your timing of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.94,0:41:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.94,0:41:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go when I'm old.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.94,0:41:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What if fate says, no, you're going this week?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.94,0:41:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to go this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.23,0:41:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So the child in you, the infant,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.23,0:41:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,insists on having its own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.23,0:41:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to leave the planet this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.51,0:41:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I got tickets to the ball game next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.51,0:41:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.51,0:41:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, somebody got a little bit ahead of me
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.51,0:41:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,about the self-inquiry situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.51,0:41:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I want to add a little bit about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.51,0:41:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.51,0:41:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,About the self-inquiry, Roman.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.51,0:41:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Which, by the way, I think it has a little bit of equivalent
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.51,0:41:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,when you mention one of your last chapters of the eye
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.51,0:42:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,about towards the realization of the self,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.51,0:42:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,asking yourself, how do I know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.51,0:42:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I know that I exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.51,0:42:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.51,0:42:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So just biting into that feelingness of beingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.38,0:42:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of I-ness, of being aware that what is.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.38,0:42:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The field of it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.38,0:42:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, just the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.38,0:42:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right, the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.38,0:42:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.38,0:42:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,F-I-E-L-D.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.38,0:42:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Being aware of that feelingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.38,0:42:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,is that, that's like a quality of divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.38,0:42:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that's like an expression of divinity within ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.38,0:42:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and that's the quality of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.38,0:42:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the source of our existence, and that's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.38,0:42:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that isn't all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.38,0:42:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there's a catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.38,0:42:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in the right state.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.38,0:42:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you've got to find the county, the city, the town,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.38,0:42:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and the right block.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.38,0:42:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the quality of experiencing that you experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.44,0:42:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the quality of subjectivity, radical subjectivity,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.44,0:42:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,reduces it to the awareness of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.44,0:43:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the what's of existence
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.44,0:43:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.44,0:43:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The source of joy is the awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.61,0:43:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,that the source of one's existence
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.61,0:43:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is innate to who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.61,0:43:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you don't have to look outside of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.61,0:43:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,for anything to make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.92,0:43:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,These flowers are not going to make me happy
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.92,0:43:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,or make me not unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.19,0:43:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,However, they're incredibly beautiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.19,0:43:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,so you enjoy them because they're witnessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.19,0:43:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But you just mentioned on this session
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.84,0:43:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that the trees are like ourselves because they are aware,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.84,0:43:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but they're just only expressed as existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.84,0:43:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,not as a beingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.84,0:43:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say trees were aware that they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.84,0:43:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Awareness that you are shows up at calibration level 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.11,0:43:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that, you are, but you're not aware that you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.36,0:43:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So below 200, life experiences life,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.36,0:44:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but it is not aware that it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.40,0:44:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a subtlety.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.94,0:44:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But quite a significant one.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.94,0:44:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Because to be aware of your own existence
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.13,0:44:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,as beingness, as existence, as life,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.30,0:44:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is a value.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.42,0:44:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So you treat others as you believe you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.42,0:44:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, a value.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.42,0:44:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So over 200, other people have a value.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.42,0:44:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You think, I'm going to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.42,0:44:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but how will the neighbors feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.42,0:44:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to paint my house bright red.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.42,0:44:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how will the neighbors feel about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.42,0:44:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't occur below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.01,0:44:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Above 200, you'd say,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.01,0:44:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,well, I don't want to upset the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.01,0:44:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want people to be unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.01,0:44:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But below 200, you're only interested in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.98,0:44:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I like a black and white and blue house.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.19,0:44:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you don't like it, it's my right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.19,0:45:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll call my lawyer and, you know, free speech,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.19,0:45:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,all the rest, free expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.51,0:45:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can paint nudes on it if I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.51,0:45:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the end, if I just abide in just that feelingness of I-ness,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.51,0:45:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that'll take care of everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.51,0:45:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a simplification.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.34,0:45:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're in the right direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.88,0:45:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To sense the context out of which one's existence arises.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.32,0:45:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And eventually, one realizes that that is closer to your reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.67,0:45:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So you pull back farther and farther from linear content
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.67,0:45:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to nonlinear context.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.67,0:45:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the nonlinear context enlarges and enlarges and enlarges.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.67,0:45:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still something of the ego left, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.71,0:45:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,despite the fact that it's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.71,0:45:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.01,0:45:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.01,0:45:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when the ego comes up to die, you'll know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.01,0:45:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the call is to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.98,0:46:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This, too, must I surrender to thee, O Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.98,0:46:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,because the core of the ego is its belief that it is the source of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.84,0:46:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So when there's nothing left in the absolute silence,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.84,0:46:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you're totally alone, the door stands before you,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.00,0:46:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and you know that the last thing you have to lay down is your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.00,0:46:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.00,0:46:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, do I surrender to thee, O Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.59,0:46:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you know that it is your life that you must surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.11,0:46:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what you believe 100% is your life, is that core of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.92,0:46:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This, too, must be surrendered to God, comes as the knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.92,0:46:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you've heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.92,0:46:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You've heard it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.92,0:46:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's imprinted as a vibration in your aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.15,0:46:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now out of the silence, the knowingness comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.59,0:46:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.23,0:46:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then arises a tremendous fear of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.23,0:46:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You've never died before.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.51,0:47:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the one and only time you can die.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.51,0:47:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The fear of death arises.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.48,0:47:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then comes the knowingness from the teacher somewhere in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.48,0:47:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that exists as a frequency in your aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.48,0:47:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That all fear is illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.17,0:47:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All fear is illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.17,0:47:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And death is not a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.17,0:47:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All fear is illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.88,0:47:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And death is not a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.88,0:47:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That calibrates at 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.92,0:47:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You got the message now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.40,0:47:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.40,0:47:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But as the moment arises,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.40,0:47:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you feel the agony of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.57,0:47:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and it lasts for a few moments,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.05,0:47:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,the one and only death that's possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.34,0:47:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and then suddenly bursts forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.36,0:47:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the information you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.55,0:48:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,See, before when you die, you just go out of body.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.55,0:48:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.55,0:48:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're up here in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.94,0:48:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The body's down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.94,0:48:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's sobbing and crying and carrying on.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.94,0:48:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.26,0:48:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.26,0:48:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm delighted to be here,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.26,0:48:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm very grateful for the truth that continues to flow through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.42,0:48:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question and a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.42,0:48:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a musician,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.67,0:48:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd like to give you this music for meditation.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.67,0:48:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.67,0:48:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,As a small gesture to give back to you some of what I've received.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.67,0:48:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.67,0:48:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Journey Within.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.67,0:48:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a nice title.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.73,0:48:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The question I have is a bit of a paradox.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.73,0:48:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you can resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.73,0:48:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,On the one hand, time is an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.96,0:48:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, in the last segment...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.01,0:48:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.01,0:48:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a track.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.01,0:48:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, when you do a tape,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.01,0:48:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,a videotape,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.01,0:48:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you can time track it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.01,0:48:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego time tracks it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.01,0:48:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Before, now, and future.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.44,0:49:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It already time tracks it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.44,0:49:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it believes in causality,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.44,0:49:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore it believes in change.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.44,0:49:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So it automatically time tracks it
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.44,0:49:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,based on sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.28,0:49:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Experience is sequential,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.28,0:49:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and it projects it that the world is sequential.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.28,0:49:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.42,0:49:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your witnessing that's sequential.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.42,0:49:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the world now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.42,0:49:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.42,0:49:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You see it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.42,0:49:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So the sequence is...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.42,0:49:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest internal, not rest external.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.76,0:49:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it kind of takes care of the rest of my question,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.76,0:49:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,because on the one hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.76,0:49:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it seemed like time is an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.76,0:49:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, in your last segment,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.76,0:49:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you said the choices that we make today
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.76,0:49:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,are different than the choices we made before,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.76,0:49:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,because we're not the same now as we were then.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.76,0:49:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah, it's not because of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.76,0:49:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of transition.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.76,0:49:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,See, everything is evolving.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.76,0:49:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So that which it is now
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.76,0:49:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is not what it was when it was just this.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.76,0:49:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to call that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.76,0:49:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,See, what you're not seeing is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.76,0:50:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're seeing is evolution
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.15,0:50:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,unfolding as emergence.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.34,0:50:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The word emergence explains it better.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.88,0:50:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.88,0:50:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the chrysalis, out of the cocoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.88,0:50:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the chrysalis emerges the butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.88,0:50:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But the pupa does not become the butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.65,0:50:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The pupa is still only a butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.92,0:50:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The pupa.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.40,0:50:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is the emergence of its potentiality
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.40,0:50:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,becoming an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.40,0:50:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't occur in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.34,0:50:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Time is a superimposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.34,0:50:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So creation is the emergence,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.28,0:50:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the unmanifest becoming manifest,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.28,0:50:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,in which the infinite potentiality of divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.28,0:50:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,comes forth as manifestation.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.69,0:50:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the physicality
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.07,0:50:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is part of the potentiality of manifestation.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.07,0:51:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.11,0:51:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.11,0:51:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergence answers your question.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.44,0:51:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergence.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.44,0:51:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.05,0:51:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.26,0:51:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.26,0:51:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.80,0:51:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,why are so many very smart people
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.80,0:51:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrate below 200 as opposed to in the 400s?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.65,0:51:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's one of integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.65,0:51:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So the intellect can be used to make bombs to kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.65,0:51:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The intellect can be used to make penicillin to save people.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.65,0:51:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So the intellect is,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.65,0:51:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.17,0:51:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is equality.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.17,0:51:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it's up to the person how to use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.40,0:51:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How to use that.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.78,0:51:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can use it to play chess.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.78,0:51:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use it to make money.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.78,0:51:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use it to,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.03,0:52:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a good doctor, lawyer, merchant, or chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.03,0:52:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you want, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.03,0:52:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you use with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.03,0:52:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's like having a very good athletic body, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.03,0:52:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can use it
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.03,0:52:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to the best of your ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.51,0:52:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have a touch?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.17,0:52:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.17,0:52:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.19,0:52:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for a wonderful lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.19,0:52:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My question regards prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.19,0:52:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And when one wants to make a major decision
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.63,0:52:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.73,0:52:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,regarding prayer and decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.73,0:52:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and some people have suggested that,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.73,0:52:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, I just pray for God's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.73,0:52:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And you talked about the power of intention and our will.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.73,0:52:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Does God,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.73,0:52:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,does God have a will as such
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.73,0:52:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,in the way that we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.73,0:52:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.73,0:53:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.46,0:53:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The best prayer,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.84,0:53:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and also the best way to do kinesiology,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.84,0:53:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is to ask what serves the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.36,0:53:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So people are saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.36,0:53:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, I pray that so-and-so gets well.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.36,0:53:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.36,0:53:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that would serve the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.36,0:53:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,May or may not.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.50,0:53:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.50,0:53:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's not going to serve her good.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.84,0:53:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Because
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.84,0:53:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,from the moment you're born,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.98,0:53:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the time of living here is already pre-set.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.03,0:53:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of karmic propensities,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.03,0:53:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you leave here in one form or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.03,0:53:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.03,0:53:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So interference could,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.44,0:53:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, not necessarily be a benefit.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.23,0:53:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.63,0:53:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.63,0:53:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,does God have a will as we,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.63,0:53:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,as such as we have a will?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.63,0:53:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We project an anthropomorphic view of will, see,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.63,0:53:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,as a partiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.63,0:53:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say God's will is more general than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.63,0:54:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shines forth out of mercy and infinite mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.88,0:54:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But within its power,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.05,0:54:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is karmically destined to potentialize
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.19,0:54:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,will potentialize.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.19,0:54:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So it isn't so much that it's God's will,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.53,0:54:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,because you hardly need to remind him
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.53,0:54:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,what his duties are.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.17,0:54:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people spend most of their time
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.17,0:54:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,advising God what's needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.17,0:54:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Aunt Nellie's gallbladder,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.78,0:54:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister Susie's,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.78,0:54:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,asthma,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.09,0:54:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and my grandfather's health.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.28,0:54:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It goes on and on,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.28,0:54:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,advising God what needs to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.28,0:54:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.03,0:54:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So if divinity is hierarchical,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.03,0:54:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,hierarchical, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.03,0:55:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I see divinity as an infinite power.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.03,0:55:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And then there's step-down transformers,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.03,0:55:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,whereby it comes down to the human domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.15,0:55:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,As I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.15,0:55:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,one glance from an archangel can fry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.15,0:55:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.15,0:55:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,even as it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.69,0:55:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,as you advance in consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.69,0:55:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,when you get around 800 or so,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.69,0:55:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you get burning agonies in your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.69,0:55:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.69,0:55:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and compared to celestial realms,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.73,0:55:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the calibration level of 800 or 850
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.73,0:55:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,around there is child's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.73,0:55:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But already it's painful within this domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.73,0:55:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you want to go on to a thousand or over,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.73,0:55:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,it's probably best to leave the body
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.73,0:55:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and go to celestial realms
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.73,0:55:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,where people don't have protoplasmic nervous systems,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.73,0:55:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.30,0:55:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.30,0:55:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So divine will then is,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.30,0:55:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.30,0:55:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,as a pragmatic interpretation,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.46,0:55:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,would be for each thing to fulfill its karmic potentiality
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.09,0:55:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,in a manner that serves the highest good,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.09,0:56:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,which does not exclude yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.57,0:56:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,nor does it exclude others.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.57,0:56:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Holy Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:05.57,0:56:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the miraculous is
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.57,0:56:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that both are simultaneously possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.57,0:56:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego sees that if I win,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.57,0:56:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.57,0:56:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Holy Spirit arranges it in such a way
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.57,0:56:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that everybody wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.50,0:56:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.50,0:56:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.13,0:56:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The angelic forces are God's working staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.80,0:56:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff members.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.92,0:56:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about the Sedona release technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.92,0:56:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The what?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.92,0:56:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sedona release technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.92,0:56:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a form of spiritual growth, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.05,0:56:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.05,0:56:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.05,0:56:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sedona method.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.05,0:56:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sedona method.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.05,0:56:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sedona release method, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.05,0:56:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.05,0:56:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.05,0:56:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was wondering if that's been calibrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.05,0:56:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to know if that's an integral.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.05,0:56:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.05,0:56:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about 480.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.05,0:57:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me do the Sedona method.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.05,0:57:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sedona method is over 480, 485.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.44,0:57:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about 480 now.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.44,0:57:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.44,0:57:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a high level of truth, 480.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.44,0:57:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.44,0:57:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Very effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.44,0:57:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.44,0:57:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.44,0:57:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The only mistake to not make with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.94,0:57:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.94,0:57:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.94,0:57:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The only mistake to not to make with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.61,0:57:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.61,0:57:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The only mistake to not to make with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.61,0:57:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.42,0:57:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The only mistake to not to make with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.42,0:57:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.42,0:57:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The only mistake to not to make with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.42,0:57:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.42,0:57:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The only mistake to not to make with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.15,0:57:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.26,0:57:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch very carefully because the downside of this is severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.51,0:57:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Love is not an attachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.36,0:57:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't confuse divine love, which is a quality of divinity, with personal love.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.92,0:57:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So one part of that school is to surrender and release on love as an attachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.11,0:57:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You then end up flat, uncaring.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.53,0:58:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's confusing divine love.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.15,0:58:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't refute love as a reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.51,0:58:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's a quality of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.13,0:58:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Personal love is an attachment, a clean, let's say.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.69,0:58:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And so surrender the attachment, possessiveness at all, but don't denigrate the value of perfection,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.53,0:58:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,beauty, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.53,0:58:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where he fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.65,0:58:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.65,0:58:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.55,0:58:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Done?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.55,0:58:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, it's a good technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.03,0:58:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.03,0:58:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.15,0:58:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Good technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.15,0:58:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't confuse personal love with divine love.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.15,0:58:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.21,0:58:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.21,0:58:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Done?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.21,0:58:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So personal love and divine love, that's the error.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.21,0:58:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you end up in the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.21,0:58:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't get to the void yet, but we will.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.21,0:58:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.21,0:58:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just really pleased to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.75,0:58:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I've come to one of your lectures as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.75,0:58:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My question has been answered by the man that approached the issue on fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.75,0:58:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So maybe I'll just avail myself of a little bit of that touch, healing touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.05,0:58:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.05,0:58:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.05,0:58:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.05,0:58:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.05,0:58:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.05,0:58:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.05,0:58:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.05,0:58:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.05,0:59:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.05,0:59:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.05,0:59:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.05,0:59:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.05,0:59:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.05,0:59:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.05,0:59:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.05,0:59:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.05,0:59:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.05,0:59:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.05,0:59:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.05,0:59:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
