Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.47,1:14:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the term that you used was the anguish of the soul, like when people are experiencing higher levels of these tractor fields and then come back out of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.57,1:14:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, when you drop, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.84,1:14:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.39,1:14:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The night of the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.31,1:14:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when people crash, sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.42,1:14:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the euphoria, when you're above your negative karma, then you're semi-euphoric.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.15,1:14:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, that may bring up, now because you're powerful enough to handle it,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.84,1:14:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,now it pulls up the dreaded.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.72,1:14:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That you have not wanted to look at.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.42,1:14:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, you feel pulled down.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.34,1:14:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, why have thou deserted me, my beloved?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.60,1:14:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning Jesus Christ, or the God, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.30,1:14:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All it means is that you've earned the right to face something even heavier.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.97,1:14:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only go as high as you've been low.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.43,1:15:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's always good to know, if you feel down, that you can only go as high as you can go down.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.47,1:15:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yeah, you can only go as high as you've been down.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.52,1:15:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.42,1:15:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the Christian saints, you know, that's very well known amongst the mystics.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.60,1:15:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,When you say you can go as high as you can go low, you mean relatively each way.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.78,1:15:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you go up 200 one way, you can only drop down, well, five or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.85,1:15:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just to make you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.43,1:15:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.94,1:15:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.56,1:15:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.77,1:15:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.73,1:15:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, when you're feeling high, and then suddenly some horrible guilt comes up,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.86,1:15:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,something that you had, you know, repressed comes up.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.56,1:15:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, suddenly, oh, my God, where did that come from?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.64,1:16:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, first of all, a stack gets repressed, in Freudian language, suppressed and repressed.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.81,1:16:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, the stacks pile up lifetime after lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.81,1:16:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when you experience a loss, it isn't this loss, it's the stack of losses.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.60,1:16:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't this person's dying in your life, it's all of them that have died in their life.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.19,1:16:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.31,1:16:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that stack comes up.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.97,1:16:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So, like the young man who was talking about fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.64,1:16:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The fear that he's experiencing is a bunch of stacks.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.85,1:16:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you want to set out the fear and let it run, it'll run out.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.46,1:16:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It could take weeks, months, days, hours, who knows.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.15,1:16:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But all the fear of all the lifetimes is like in a compressed tank.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.10,1:16:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.43,1:16:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.35,1:16:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a pleasure to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.89,1:16:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have a question regarding the angelic power.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.81,1:16:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.14,1:16:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I was raised a Roman Catholic back in Poland.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.80,1:16:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And I always had pictures of guardian angels.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.26,1:17:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've read your books.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.89,1:17:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've read about 50,000 plus about archangels.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.85,1:17:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me a little bit more about angels?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.81,1:17:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you care about angels?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.42,1:17:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Worry about who you are in the here and now.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.60,1:17:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.14,1:17:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.69,1:17:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's maiden-esque, and it's charming, to invoke the angels, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.89,1:17:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But you remain who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.53,1:17:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, asking for divinity in the form of angels, you're really asking God.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.14,1:17:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really asking God, who, like a step-down transformer, communicates better with humans
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.82,1:17:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,at that level we call angelic.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.64,1:17:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.64,1:17:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.64,1:18:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But angels are also embodied.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.27,1:18:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The gentleman up here from the 12-step group.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.96,1:18:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He was talking about angelic people, and I've had angels stop and help me over and over
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.88,1:18:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,in this lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.88,1:18:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And I remember asking with the arm, was that an angel in the body?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.03,1:18:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.42,1:18:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You think angels are all dead little spirits flying around with flowers and wings.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.42,1:18:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.42,1:18:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The angelic.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.42,1:18:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a million miles from nowhere when a truck...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.42,1:18:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I was in my truck, and a truck pulled over next to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.72,1:18:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on a terrible interchange.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.18,1:18:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like that, but I had a plane to catch.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.68,1:18:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.69,1:18:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Broken down, middle of an interchange.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.46,1:18:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No phone, no communication.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.46,1:18:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, the pickup truck stops and says, how can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.61,1:18:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He took my tire off.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.84,1:18:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He put it in his pickup truck.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.19,1:18:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He went to the nearest exit, went to a station, had it fixed, cloverleaf back, cloverleaf
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.27,1:18:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,back, and came over.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.27,1:18:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you explain that?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.65,1:18:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That was an angel.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:56.65,1:18:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.35,1:19:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That completely answers my question.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.73,1:19:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There's angels here and now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.34,1:19:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.97,1:19:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.47,1:19:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There's angels in the earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.97,1:19:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they come in and out of body.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.67,1:19:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They come in and out of body.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.46,1:19:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no question.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.46,1:19:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to offer you a hug, if I could.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.72,1:19:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.72,1:19:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.72,1:19:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No hugs.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.72,1:19:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No hugs.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.72,1:19:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I have broken vertebrae.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.72,1:19:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.72,1:19:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.72,1:19:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My vertebrae have turned to styrofoam, and therefore no hugs.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.72,1:19:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.88,1:19:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,However, they're getting stronger by the day.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.88,1:19:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.84,1:19:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty soon, I'll have calcium toxicity, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.09,1:19:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Over calcium, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.09,1:19:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How's your bones?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.09,1:19:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.09,1:19:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.09,1:19:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.09,1:19:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.09,1:19:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.09,1:20:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, thank you for being the lighthouse, because it was hard not to know the way out
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.96,1:20:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.96,1:20:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It was nice to know the way out.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.31,1:20:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for pointing it out for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.31,1:20:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I really appreciate it, personally.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.10,1:20:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And well, I wanted to comment.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.00,1:20:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When you were talking about people below 200 are not aware of their existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.46,1:20:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.59,1:20:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I belong to a 12-step group.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.59,1:20:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.59,1:20:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.59,1:20:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,12-step group.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.59,1:20:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,12-step.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.59,1:20:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.59,1:20:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.59,1:20:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.59,1:20:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.59,1:20:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And a few months after I started applying the spiritual principles to my daily life,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.78,1:20:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in a meeting, and all of the sudden, I was very aware.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.59,1:20:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.59,1:20:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All of the sudden, I become aware of my existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.59,1:20:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was like, I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.59,1:20:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.59,1:20:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.59,1:20:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was like...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.59,1:20:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Pantalo.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:51.53,1:20:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I was like, raising my hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.53,1:20:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I need to share this.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.77,1:20:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We are.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.77,1:20:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.77,1:20:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.77,1:20:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They were questioning my sobriety.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.77,1:21:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They were like, I haven't smoked anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.77,1:21:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear you...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.77,1:21:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.77,1:21:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We are.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:03.77,1:21:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.77,1:21:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.77,1:21:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.77,1:21:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The source of joy is innate as one's existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.77,1:21:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not dependent on anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.77,1:21:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.77,1:21:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.77,1:21:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.77,1:21:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.77,1:21:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.77,1:21:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.19,1:21:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.19,1:21:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.19,1:21:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:18.19,1:21:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.19,1:21:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.19,1:21:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.19,1:21:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.19,1:21:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.73,1:21:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.73,1:21:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.51,1:21:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.51,1:21:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.51,1:21:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.51,1:21:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.51,1:21:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like you, if you want to say anything to those...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.63,1:21:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we're just a very little group of students that are, they have the grace to
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.71,1:21:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,be exposed to the presence of the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.85,1:22:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the students are not able to be exposed to the presence of the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.35,1:22:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,can get the material through tapes through the books but they don't have
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.22,1:22:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the the the karmic grace to be exposed to the presence to the teacher would you
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.07,1:22:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,say something for them no okay when the time arises the impulse arises the
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.35,1:22:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,opportunity arises you know I spent days with Ramana let's see I spent the time
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.43,1:22:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,with the many of the Matkananda and Ramesh Bhalsakar and various people see
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.92,1:22:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the Karmapa various people like that see so when you're attracted to it somehow
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.26,1:22:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the opportunity arises and you feel compelled to do that but having
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.38,1:22:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,completed that there's no compulsion to see him again so if Ramesh is back in
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.81,1:22:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,town I don't feel like I must quickly go and salute him but I remember the
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.85,1:23:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,encounter was right at the question level at
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.19,1:23:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,18 and I remember the encounter was right at the question level at 18 and I
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.39,1:23:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,remember the encounter was right at the question level at 18 and I remember the
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.42,1:23:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,part 2 that we lose theressed 12 to be 50 of whether existence and non-existence
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.03,1:23:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,are realities or perceptions we started out right there so that's funny because
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.32,1:23:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that's what I was born with at age 3 suddenly the witness to existence was
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.06,1:23:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the ultimate reality existence or nothingness was the ultimate reality the
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.14,1:23:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,void the misunderstanding of the teaching of the Buddha or was it illness hit me
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.77,1:23:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,at age 3 out of nothingness that was the dilemma
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.93,1:23:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And here, many decades later, I'm talking to Randy, we open up with that with each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.64,1:23:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,One time, a person was in a lecture I was giving, and he had been hopelessly alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.97,1:24:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle of the lecture, his consciousness jumped 150 points.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.84,1:24:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He became sober, stayed sober.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.14,1:24:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what had gone on with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.18,1:24:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, six weeks later, a couple months later, a truck pulls up, a pickup truck, to
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.56,1:24:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,the house, the little house where I was living.
