Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.47,1:24:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This incredible table, weighed a ton, I still have it, it's right in the middle of the living.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.97,1:24:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And in there in Sanskrit, he's got written, allness and nothingness in Sanskrit.
