Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.92,1:26:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick question.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.92,1:26:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It hit me at one year old that our true reality is pure happiness and peace and joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.07,1:26:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.07,1:26:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.30,1:26:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've been asking myself since, why are we dreaming about being less than what
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.30,1:26:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is the truth?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.30,1:26:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you're believing.
