Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.89,1:26:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She says, you know, our true.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.89,1:26:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,About being less than what is the truth of who we are.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.97,1:26:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, happiness and joy and it's what meant for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.97,1:26:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say that it's dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.97,1:26:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's only a style of presentation of the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.21,1:26:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're saying is that it is not based on reality, which I agree.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.30,1:26:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.39,1:26:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So why are we.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.39,1:26:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the evolution of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.39,1:27:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The dominion of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.39,1:27:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Dominion of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.59,1:27:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Which thinks like an animal.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.59,1:27:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the spiritual reality has not superseded the animal consciousness completely.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:15.10,1:27:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The linear still tends to predominate and the reality is in the non-linear dimension.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.84,1:27:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.84,1:27:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,As you relinquish the belief in the reality of the linear, then you see that the reality
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.53,1:27:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is the non-linear.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.53,1:27:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And that the only reality the linear has is the presence of the non-linear within it.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.53,1:27:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.52,1:27:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll move right along.
